title: Central Corridor
clause_text: Central Corridor.- From Regal Cinema junction to V.N.Purav Marg, Trombay, covering Mahatma Gandhi Road, DadabhaiNavroji Road, LokmanyaTilak Road, Dr.B. Ambedkar Marg, Sion Road, Tatya Tope Road, V.N. Purav Marg uptoAnushakti Nagar.
